answersResultList.title: Somewhat Leo.
answersResultList.resultContent: If you're a sucker for the colors of autumn, you're somewhat Leo. Like the Lion, you're a social animal, but you'd rather spend time with your core group instead of expanding your circle. Maybe you can't be bothered with going that extra mile, or maybe you're afraid of what you'll find when you get there. As much as you enjoy your work, you won't let it rule your life if a better offer comes along. And even when you have a lot to give, there are limits to your generosity. What if you can't replace what you just gave away?

answersResultList.title: Not very Leo.
answersResultList.resultContent: Leo is all about warmth, but your idea of keeping warm isn't very Leo - huddling under the covers instead of turning up the heat, or cozying up indoors when it's cold or rainy outside. You like the quiet life, and close relationships are often too demanding for you. Maybe you actively avoid other people, or maybe you prefer to watch them without getting involved. You're not very comfortable when all eyes are upon you. Even among friends you worry about failing to meet expectations. You're more likely to follow than lead, and that isn't very Leo at all!

answersResultList.title: Mostly Leo.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're outgoing and optimistic. You're always ready to improve yourself or your circumstances, while a true Leo would be self-assured instead of hopeful. But no worries, hope is a great motivator, and 'I could' is almost as powerful as 'I will.' Readiness is everything. You're open to possibilities, and willing to host any miracle that might happen on your turf. If you're not already in a relationship, the gods of love are totally welcome to bring it on. If you are in a relationship, you probably let your partner take the lead. And he or she appreciates it!

Maybe you can't be bothered with going that extra mile, or maybe you're afraid of what you'll find when you get there. As much as you enjoy your work, you won't let it rule your life if a better offer comes along. And even when you have a lot to give, there are limits to your generosity. What if you can't replace what you just gave away?

answersResultList.title: Mostly Leo.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're outgoing and optimistic. You're always ready to improve yourself or your circumstances, while a true Leo would be self-assured instead of hopeful. But no worries, hope is a great motivator, and 'I could' is almost as powerful as 'I will.' Readiness is everything. You're open to possibilities, and willing to host any miracle that might happen on your turf. If you're not already in a relationship, the gods of love are totally welcome to bring it on. If you are in a relationship, you probably let your partner take the lead. And he or she appreciates it!

answersResultList.title: True Leo.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're hot in every sense of the word. Maybe you're in demand and everybody loves you. And if not, who cares? You feel so good about yourself that you won't hold it against them. There's always an audience for you somewhere, and any kind of relationship thrives when the other person recognizes that about you. As a Lion, once you establish your territory you'll defend it with everything you have. That territory includes family, romance, friendship, and business. Your loyalty is off the charts. And so is your entertainment value. Whatever you're delivering, there's more where that came from.
